The number of eligible patients is small, and we have therefore adopted a Bayesian inferential framework for this trial, which has been described in detail in another publication [37]. The primary endpoint is the log odds ratio of 90-day survival after major trauma centre treatment with REBOA, compared to major trauma centre treatment alone:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
